<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= @title %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    h1 { color: #333; }
    a {
      color: #0066cc;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .demo-link {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background-color: #0066cc;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .demo-link:hover {
      background-color: #0052a3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>SoliLang LiveView Demo</h1>
  <p>Welcome to the SoliLang framework with LiveView support!</p>
  <p>LiveView enables real-time, server-rendered HTML with no JavaScript build step.</p>

  <a href="/counter" class="demo-link">Try LiveView Counter</a>
</body>
</html>
